data.description:
Come and make this beautiful, updated townhome in Stony Creek yours today. It backs to green belt and sets in a Cul-de-sac.
2 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms. Main floor features Kitchen with SS appliances, dining area, laundry, access to the garage, ½ bath. From the living room with fireplace you can access the large fenced back yard for your enjoyment. large windows, high vaulted ceilings and skylights. Upstairs there are 2 bedrooms, full bath, open loft with build in book cases. The primary bedroom has closet organizers, vaulted ceilings and a sink. A/C, tankless water heater. There are also trails, creek and open spaces around. Close to shopping, dining, Chatfield state park, Major Highways Welcome home today.
